    "However, LLMs can still disregard provided information and rely on their parametric knowledge due to intrinsic mechanisms (Jin et al., 2024; Xu et al., 2024a) or sensitivity to prompts (Liu et al., 2024).",
    "Another solution is adapting the generation process-referred to as decoding-to produce more factual responses (Lee et al., 2022; Burns et al., 2023; Moschella et al., 2023; Li et al., 2023a; Chuang et al., 2023), and post-editing to refine the originally generated content, leveraging the self-correction capabilities of LLMs (Dhuliawala et al., 2023; Ji et al., 2023b).",
